This paper deals with optimizing the load balancing in LTE networks, which falls under the category of network optimization and management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also uses Multi-Objective Particle Swarm Optimization (MO-PSO) which is a machine learning technique, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also deals with dynamic optimization, which falls under the category of control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) another possible category. The paper also deals with optimization and balancing, which falls under the category of information theory, making cs.IT (Information Theory) another possible category. Finally, the paper uses optimization techniques to improve network performance, which falls under the category of machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category.
